{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO838901BTC0613P0D1N000296", "chronotag": "1739874690818", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "296", "numeroOrdreDepot": "296", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "AN", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO838901BTC0613P0D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PIONANR5L17BTC0613", "triAmendement": "biaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaauvm", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA793094", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845425", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "M.&#160;Ray"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "Article PREMIER", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. PREMIER", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE PREMIER", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/0613.asp#D_Article_1er"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"avant_A_Apres": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "numero": "63", "alineaDesignation": "Alin\u00e9a 63"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Supprimer l&#x2019;alin&#x00E9;a&nbsp;63.</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>La r&#x00E9;forme des retraites de 2023 a cr&#x00E9;&#x00E9; un nouveau motif de d&#x00E9;part anticip&#x00E9; en retraite pour les&nbsp;assur&#x00E9;s reconnus inaptes au travail.&nbsp;</p><p>Or, la r&#x00E9;daction de la pr&#x00E9;sente proposition de loi vise &#x00E0; revenir sur c&nbsp;avanc&#x00E9;een supprimant la mention de l'article L. 351&#x2011;1&#x2011;5 du code du travail qui permet, pour les salari&#x00E9;s reconnus inaptesde partir de mani&#x00E8;re anticip&#x00E9;e en retraite. Cette suppression entrainerait de nouvelles in&#x00E9;galit&#x00E9;s que nous ne pouvons&nbsp;pas accepter.</p><p>En effet, l&#x2019;inaptitude m&#x00E9;dicale au travail e&nbsp;reconnue&nbsp;par le m&#x00E9;decin du travail lorsque le salari&#x00E9; ne peut&nbsp;pas poursuivre l&#x2019;exercice de son emploi sans nuire gravement &#x00E0; sa sant&#x00E9; physique ou mentale.&nbsp;En supprimant l'ouverture au droit de retraite anticip&#x00E9; pour ces cat&#x00E9;gories de travailleurs, les auteurs de la proposition de loi viendront restreindre les&nbsp;droits de ces individus d&#x00E9;j&#x00E0; fragilis&#x00E9;s.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2024-11-25", "datePublication": "2024-11-27", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "AC", "libelle": "A discuter"}, "sousEtat": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "dateSort": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "sort": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO838901BTC0613P0D1N000296?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"codeLoi": "0", "divisionCodeLoi": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"idDiscussion": "74450", "typePosition": "Milieu"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}